| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4752 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7ffb0ec8-029a-55fd-a6e8-5c4655800ed6"
